flowchart TD
    Start([Device Setup]) --> Power[Power On Device]
    Power --> EnterProv[Enter Provisioning Mode]
    EnterProv --> GenQR[Generate QR Code]
    GenQR --> Display[Display Pairing Info]
    Display --> Scan{Technician Scans?}
    Scan -- Timeout --> Expire[Pairing Expired]
    Expire --> Start
    Scan -- Yes --> Central[Central Validates]
    Central --> Valid{Valid?}
    Valid -- No --> Retry[Retry]
    Retry --> Display
    Valid -- Yes --> Push[Push Configuration]
    Push --> Apply[Apply Config]
    Apply --> Test[Test Connection]
    Test --> OK{Connection OK?}
    OK -- No --> Retry
    OK -- Yes --> Complete[Provisioning Complete]
    Complete --> End([Device Online])
